{
  "stem": "21582.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, and she suffered tremendous hunger and dislocation and persecution.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then she had a few good years, relatively good years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then the second war came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My mother imbued us with a love for beauty, a love for life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My mother never passed a flower or a cloud in the sky that she would not-- oh, how beautiful it is!",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Oh, how wonderful it is!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She did not have much formal education.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But she was very much involved in what was going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She loved the opera.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And she would-- I remember when she would go to the opera, she would just float into the house and just sing the arias and tell us-- usually it was the morning after-- and tell us the stories the-- of, of the operas word by word, action by action.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We lived-- we were really ordinary people-- middle-class people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We practiced the typical, good, middle-class values.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There was a lot of love in our immediate family and surrounding and extended family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We lived on a nice, middle-class street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "In the street-- the houses on our street-- well, actually, they were buildings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Warsaw was an ancient city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I say 'was' because you know that Warsaw was totally, totally destroyed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And so whatever we see now, what people see now in Warsaw as the old city is really a city on top of a city.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It really-- whatever was isn't anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The houses on our street stood sort of like shoulder to shoulder, and they formed long blocks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The-- we had-- most of the houses had big iron gates.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Now, I don't know if all of them had big iron gates.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But this is what stands out in my memory.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
